snippet.title: Protone Pedals Attack Overdrive
snippet.description:
Protone is running a Black Friday weekend sale for this pedal: http://protonepedals.com/blackfriday/

Jeff Holcomb and I put this video together as I have gotten a lot of people asking me to demo the pedal and also showcase what it can do.

This goes over the various applications of the pedal, and I hope this shows just how versatile and unique this pedal is!

Signal Chain is: Jackson Custom Shop 7 with BKP Juggernaut Pickups and D'addario NYXL Strings.
Protone Attack Overdrive
Peavey 6534+
Two Notes Torpedo Live (used as an attenuator and to send direct signal to Axefx)
Axefx II XL (used only as a cab sim with a Custom Zilla 2x12 IR)
Zilla 2x12 Fatboy with Celestion V30/Creamback H Combo.
Connected with Planet Waves American Stage Cables.

No post processing or eq applied to guitar tone.
